Class AddressDTO

java.lang.Object
it.uninsubria.dto.AddressDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AddressDTO extends Object implements Serializable
Data Transfer Object for Address information. This class is responsible for encapsulating address data to transfer between client and server. Uses public fields for direct access with minimal constructors for different use cases.
Author:
Lorenzo Radice, 753252, CO
